*Redesign a well-known logo, giving it a fresh, modern, or playful touch while retaining its core identity. Think about colors, shapes, and overall aesthetics that align with the brand but add a new flair. This challenge is all about breathing new life into something iconic.*

In this task, you are supposed to Redesign the logo of **Twitter**. Submit the Illustrator file (.ai file) or a text file with a Figma link.

